{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2266c80b25","title":"关于土特产品收购工作和统战工作的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5250d66c9f","index":0,"year":1956,"month":11,"day":24,"articleId":"2266c80b25"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"a2f6c6af57","name":"陈云","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"09216c2c44","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2266c80b25","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈云，当时任中共中央副主席、国务院副总理兼商业部部长。李维汉，当时任中共中央统战部部长。"},{"id":"aad13b3d3d","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2266c80b25","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指新华社《内部参考》1956年11月21日第二〇五七期上刊载的河北省建屏县贸易系统有些单位，在收购农民土特产品时压秤压价，非法营利，引起农民不满的消息。"},{"id":"f1f9825986","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2266c80b25","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指同期《内部参考》刊载的武汉民主人士就甸牙利事件对我统战工作提出意见的消息。消息说，武汉民主人士希望中共从句牙利事件中接受经验教训，进一步改进统战工作，采取措施改变“五统五不统”的现象。"},{"id":"4bc1ee90a0","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2266c80b25","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是当时武汉民主人士中对中共统战工作的意见的一种说法。五统五不统，是指统上不统下、统大不统小、统工商不统党派、统进步不统落后、统政治不统思想。"}],"contents":[{"id":"cabe5f33e0","type":"title","text":"关于土特产品收购工作和统战工作的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2266c80b25"},{"id":"09216c2c44","type":"paragraph","text":"送陈云、李维汉同志阅，退毛。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2266c80b25"},{"id":"aad13b3d3d","type":"paragraph","text":"请陈云同志看建屏一条消息，我看这种情况，在全国是相当多的，应当统一加以处理。请维汉看武汉的一条消息可","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2266c80b25"},{"id":"f1f9825986","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2266c80b25"},{"id":"4bc1ee90a0","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2266c80b25"},{"id":"3718332228","type":"paragraph","text":"请李维汉同志电话询问武汉什么叫五统五不统”。并要你改善工作。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2266c80b25"}],"page":{"id":"711831a766","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"2266c80b25","start":151,"end":152}}}},"__N_SSG":true}